# Deployment & Environment

## Git Workflow
- Repo: `github.com/jordanmok88/Evair-H5`
- **Production branch**: `main` → deploys to `https://evair-h5.netlify.app`
- **Feature branch**: `feature/api-integration` → `https://feature-api-integration--evair-h5.netlify.app`
- Test mode: append `?testmode=1` to any URL
- Git author: `Jordan Mok <jordanmok@Jordans-MacBook-Air.local>`
- Git config must be set per-repo (not global): `git config user.name` / `user.email`

## Three-Way Sync (ALWAYS do all three after EVERY change — see `auto-save-workflow.mdc`)
1. **Git**: `git add -A && git commit && git push origin feature/api-integration`
2. **iCloud**: `rsync -av --exclude='node_modules' --exclude='.git' --exclude='dist' "Evair-H5/" "~/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/Evair-H5-Backup/"`
3. **Local**: Already on Desktop (source of truth)

**Do NOT ask for permission to push. Auto-push after every change.**

## Netlify
- Auto-deploys on push (GitHub integration)
- Branch deploys enabled for feature branches
- Build command: `npm run build` → outputs to `dist/`
- Serverless functions in `netlify/functions/`

## Logo & Assets
- Logo: `public/evairsim-logo.png`
- Email logo: `evairsim-logo-v2.png` (CDN cache bust)
- Company website: `evairdigital.com`
